            "option-description": "<p>Use fieldsets to group related form controls. The first element inside a fieldset must be a <code>legend</code> element that describes the group.</p><ul><li>The <code>&lt;legend&gt;</code> element has had all styling removed so use appropriate heading tags or other font styling to match your form structure.</li></ul>",
