            "option-anchor": "textarea-counter",
            "option-description": "<ul><li>Allows for multiple lines of text with a character limit counter.</li><li>There may be multiple textareas with limit counters of varying lengths on one page.</li><li>Warns the user when the character limit is exceeded.</li><li>The textarea must have the class <code>limit-counter</code>.</li><li>The textarea must have the attribute <code>maxlength='[limit]'</code>, this sets the character limit.</li><li>There must be an adjacent element with the class <code>.textarea_feedback</code>.</li></ul>",
